_aChangeLog.text: removed & replaced the 2 bhop bonuses with a better bhop bonus
removed multiple other bonuses due to various issues or exploits
added _ksf prefix to prevent different versions causing issues

_sText:
maxvel 10k

Fun project made my be and some friends with a design based off my bhop map, enlightened2.

This wasn't intended to be a serious map but it turned out pretty good with a simple but effective aesthetic. The main map is a tier 1 linear, the bonuses vary from 1 to 5/6.

This will likely be my last surf-related map, thank you to everyone in the ksf/surf community in general who helped me!
